metadata.name: Free soul
metadata.external_url: That feeling of liberation, is an emotion that I carry in my stomach when I leave behind the ties of some unfortunate circumstance, and this emotion grows from deep inside me and blooms, making me feel a tingle when I see the new shoots of confidence that allow me to start from scratch and be reborn, while I let myself be guided by my impulses, and simply flow, flow like the wind.
